data.description: Please join us for an open house on Saturday 4/20 from 1pm-4pm. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this stunning five-bedroom single-family ranch-style home! This residence epitomizes modern comfort and convenience, boasting a seamless blend of elegance and functionality. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light accentuated by cathedral ceilings, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere. The spacious layout effortlessly flows from room to room, offering a sense of openness and warmth. The heart of the home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, which seamlessly integrates with the family room, perfect for entertaining. Adorned with updated fixtures, the kitchen features a breakfast nook, an island, light countertops complemented by stylish grey/blue cabinets, and stainless steel appliances, creating a contemporary and chic ambiance. Each of the bedrooms is accompanied by its own ensuite bathroom, ensuring utmost privacy and convenience for all residents. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting ample natural light streaming in through three large windows. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like haven, complete with double vanities, a luxurious garden tub, a generously-sized walk-in closet, and a standalone shower featuring three shower heads, offering a truly indulgent experience. Step outside to discover your own private oasis, where a patio awaits with an outdoor fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings under the stars. Overlooking the serene in-ground pool and sprawling lot, this outdoor space offers endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation. Situated on a generous one-acre lot, this home provides ample space for outdoor activities and enjoyment, making it an ideal haven for those seeking both tranquility and luxury. Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite ranch-style home yours - schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of refined living!
